items.title: Fake Fedex Email Delivers Donuts!, (Fri, Feb 27th)
items.content: <article>It’s Friday, let’s have a look at another simple piece of malware to close a busy week! I received a Fedex notification about a delivery. Usually, such emails are simple phishing attacks that redirect you to a fake login page to collect your credentials. Here, it was a bit different:</article>
